Installation Instructions
*************************

1. After unpacking the tar.gz file, cd to the sinsy directory.

2. Run configure script with appropriate options.

   % ./configure \
     --with-hts-engine-header-path=~/HyperVoice/hts_engine/include \
     --with-hts-engine-library-path=~/HyperVoice/hts_engine/lib

   For detail, please see.

   % ./configure --help

3. Run make.

   % make

4. Install library and binary.

   % make install
